'''2013年－2014年柬埔寨示威'''（{{lang-km|បាតុកម្មប្រឆាំងរាជរដ្ឋាភិបាល}}）是2013年7月至2014年7月期間以[[柬埔寨救國黨|柬埔寨救國黨]]為首的[[柬埔寨|柬埔寨]]反對派發起的抗議活動。2013年7月，反對派指責政府操控[[2013年柬埔寨大選|選舉]]，因此拒絕參加[[柬埔寨國民議會|國會]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Cambodia opposition boycott opening of parliament|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-24177265|work=BBC News|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2019-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191017005959/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-24177265|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於[[金邊|金邊]]舉行大型示威，反對由[[柬埔寨首相|首相]][[洪森|洪森]]領導的政府<ref name=aljazeera>{{cite web|title=Cambodia rejects call for poll fraud inquiry|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2013/07/201373083046618367.html|work=Al Jazeera|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627084214/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2013/07/201373083046618367.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。示威持續到了2013年12月<ref>{{cite news|last=Dara|first=Mech|title=CNRP Holds Biggest Demonstration in Decades|url=http://www.cambodiadaily.com/featured-stories/cnrp-holds-biggest-demonstration-in-decades-49558/|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Cambodia Daily|date=2013-12-23|archive-date=2014-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140106214930/http://www.cambodiadaily.com/featured-stories/cnrp-holds-biggest-demonstration-in-decades-49558/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，之後政府在2014年1月進行清場行動並禁止集會，直至1個月後解禁。最後政府與反對派達成協議，救國黨議員於2014年8月宣誓就職。

除了反對派，也有其他群體加入示威行列，表達訴求（如爭取調高最低工資的工人），但也有人在示威期間宣洩[[反越情緒|反越情緒]]，向[[越南裔柬埔寨人|越南人]]施暴。

== 緣由 ==
{{see also|2013年柬埔寨大選}}
{{Quote box|quote = （大選）有許多違規行為，甚至在投票日之前就暴露出來了。我們知道大局已定；執政黨這樣籌辦選舉，就是為了在投票日之前保證自己獲勝。<ref>{{cite web|last=Marks|first=Simon|title=Ruling party reels after Cambodia vote|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/07/2013729111720661730.html|work=Al Jazeera|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-09-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906162431/https://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/features/2013/07/2013729111720661730.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>|source = 救國黨黨魁[[桑蘭西|桑蘭西]]|width = 25%|align = left}}

2013年7月28日，柬埔寨舉行大選，執政的[[柬埔寨人民黨|柬埔寨人民黨]]贏得國民議會68席，宣布獲勝<ref>{{cite web|title=Cambodia opposition claims massive poll fraud|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2013/07/201372931511970482.html|work=Al Jazeera|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627084153/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/asia-pacific/2013/07/201372931511970482.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要反對黨[[柬埔寨救國黨|柬埔寨救國黨]]贏得55席，但宣稱大選出現違規行為，拒絕承認選舉結果，並抵制國會開幕儀式<ref>{{cite news|last=Fuller|first=Thomas|title=Cambodian Opposition Rejects Election Results|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/30/world/asia/cambodian-opposition-rejects-election-results.html?_r=0|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The New York Times|date=2013-07-29|archive-date=2020-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200630185332/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/30/world/asia/cambodian-opposition-rejects-election-results.html?_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Thul|first=Prak Chan|title=Cambodian opposition boycotts parliament, Hun Sen remains PM|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/23/us-cambodia-politics-idUSBRE98M02K20130923|work=Reuters|date=2013-09-23|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924185112/http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/09/23/us-cambodia-politics-idUSBRE98M02K20130923|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歐盟和美國對可能存在的選舉舞弊行為表示關注<ref name=aljazeera />，而國際[[非政府組織|非政府組織]][[人權觀察|人權觀察]]則要求進行「獨立調查」，調查關於選舉舞弊行為的指控<ref>{{cite web|title=Cambodia: Ruling Party Orchestrated Vote Fraud|url=http://www.hrw.org/news/2013/07/31/cambodia-ruling-party-orchestrated-vote-fraud|work=Human Rights Watch|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211040558/https://www.hrw.org/news/2013/07/31/cambodia-ruling-party-orchestrated-vote-fraud|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當年12月，反對黨在金邊舉行大規模示威，包括電單車集會<ref name=rfa >{{cite web|title=Cambodian Opposition Party Defies Authorities With More Protests|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/rally-12162013181645.html|work=Radio Free Asia|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125144635/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/rally-12162013181645.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。政府表示有關示威是非法集會，並宣稱他們實在「鼓動無政府狀態」<ref name=rfa />。

== 暴力行動和後續事件 == 
2014年1月3日（星期五），軍警在金邊市郊菩森芷區永盛路向示威的製衣廠工人開火，至少4人身亡，逾20人受傷<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/workers-police-clash-leaving-3-dead-in-cambodia/1822721.html|title=Workers, Police Clash, Leaving 3 Dead in Cambodia|publisher=VOA Khmer|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-date=2016-03-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317055410/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/workers-police-clash-leaving-3-dead-in-cambodia/1822721.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Sokha|first=Cheang|title=Crackdown turns deadly|url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/crackdown-turns-deadly|work=The Phnom Penh Post|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201054020/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/crackdown-turns-deadly|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Soenthrith|first=Saing|title=Five Killed During Protest Confirmed as Garment Workers|url=http://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/five-killed-during-protest-confirmed-as-garment-workers-50141/|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Cambodia Daily|date=2014-01-06|archive-date=2019-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190712140901/https://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/five-killed-during-protest-confirmed-as-garment-workers-50141/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。示威者阻塞道路，又把瓶子和石頭扔向警察，以報復警察當日稍早時對其他示威者和僧侶施暴<ref>{{cite web|title=Cambodia garment workers killed in clashes with police|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25585054|work=BBC News|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021320/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-25585054|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=democracy_unraveled >{{cite news|last=Quinlan|first=Daniel|title=Democracy unraveling|url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/video/democracy-unraveling|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Phnom Penh Post|date=2014-01-04|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126211439/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/video/democracy-unraveling|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於政府拒絕把最低工資調高到每月160美元，工人發起罷工<ref>{{cite web|last=Kunthear|first=Mom|title=Exodus follows violent clash|url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/exodus-follows-violent-clash|work=The Phnom Penh Post|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201128203809/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/exodus-follows-violent-clash|dead-url=no}}</ref>。示威者的[[反越情緒|反越情緒]]非常高漲，並對[[越南裔柬埔寨人|越南裔柬埔寨人]]施暴，令一家由越裔經營的咖啡店遭到破壞<ref name=vietnamese_violence>{{cite news|last=Reaksmey|first=Hul|title=Vietnamese Shop Near Protest Site Looted by Demonstrators|url=http://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/vietnamese-shop-near-protest-site-looted-by-demonstrators-50139/|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Cambodia Daily|date=2014-01-06|archive-date=2019-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620155600/https://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/vietnamese-shop-near-protest-site-looted-by-demonstrators-50139/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

鎮壓行動展開前數天，首相[[洪森|洪森]]前往[[越南|越南社會主義共和國]]，進行國事訪問。反對派指控洪森首相此舉意在尋求越南軍事援助。救國黨副主席[[根索卡|根索卡]]表示，洪森可能藉着這次訪問，尋求越南支持，好讓他繼續掌權，又說首相應該和柬埔寨人商議國家的問題，而不是和外國領袖商議<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/visit-12232013231824.html|title=Cambodian PM to Visit Vietnam Amid Political Tensions at Home|publisher=''Radio Free Asia''|date=2013-12-23|accessdate=2014-02-19|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126032348/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/visit-12232013231824.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月4日，柬埔寨當局進入主要示威陣地，以武力驅散示威者，但造成4人死亡<ref name=voacambodia />。當局又禁止示威者繼續示威<ref name=democracy_unraveled /><ref name=voacambodia>{{cite web|title=Cambodia Authorities Raid Protest Camp, Ban Further Demonstrations|url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodia-authorities-raid-protest-camp-ban-further-demonstrations/1823392.html|work=VOA Khmer|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320041510/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodia-authorities-raid-protest-camp-ban-further-demonstrations/1823392.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，金邊市法院也以煽動罷工，「擾亂社會秩序」為由，把反對派領袖傳召到法院問話<ref>{{cite news|last=White|first=Stuart|title=Leadership of CNRP digging in|url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/leadership-cnrp-digging|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Phnom Penh Post|date=2014-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126175504/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/leadership-cnrp-digging|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月27日，[[蜂巢電台|蜂巢電台]]台長[[蒙蘇農多|蒙蘇農多]]不理金邊市政府反對，發動示威，和示威者遊行到新聞部，要求政府開放頻譜，以便開辦電視台、擴大蜂巢電台的收聽範圍<ref name="sinchew"/>。此前，新聞部長{{en-link|喬干那烈|Khieu Kanharith}}已經以無線電頻譜已預留予未來的數碼電視頻道為由，拒絕批准蒙蘇農多擴大業務範圍的請求<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.camsinchew.com/node/34956?tid=5|title=蒙蘇農多：市府雖不批‧27日照樣示威|work=柬埔寨星洲日報|date=2014-01-25|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714230205/http://www.camsinchew.com/node/34956?tid=5|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。防暴警察之後用煙霧彈和電棒驅散示威者，而蘇農多則聲言會繼續示威，直至政府批准其請求為止。他在3月31日再舉行示威，意圖遊行到民主廣場，但同樣被防暴警察驅散，至少5人受傷。後來蘇農多露面，並呼籲示威者解散<ref name="sinchew">{{cite news|url=http://www.camsinchew.com/node/35857|title=蜂巢電台支持者上街游行‧警驅離衝突5人傷|work=柬埔寨星洲日報|date=2014-04-01|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714171312/http://www.camsinchew.com/node/35857|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

示威禁令在當年2月解除，不過洪森警告未來他會動員自己的支持者舉行聚會，抗衡任何由反對黨發動的反政府示威<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/cambodia-lifts-ban-on/1013470.html|title=Cambodia lifts ban on demonstrations|publisher=''Channel NewsAsia''|date=2014-02-26|accessdate=2014-02-27|archive-date=2014-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140306223928/http://www.channelnewsasia.com/news/asiapacific/cambodia-lifts-ban-on/1013470.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年7月8日，示威者在金邊[[越南|越南]]大使館門前聚集，抗議1949年[[下高棉人|下高棉]]領土被讓與越南（此領土變更具有爭議），呼籲越南道歉。越南大使館在7月9日發表聲明，呼籲柬埔寨尊重越南的主權和獨立，拒絕道歉<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rfa.org/khmer/news/politics/vn-denies-apoligize-khmerkrom-07082014224017.html |script-title=km:វៀតណាមបដិសេធមិនសុំទោសរឿងបំភ្លៃប្រវត្តិសាស្ត្រខ្មែរកម្ពុជាក្រោម |publisher=[[自由亞洲電台|Radio Free Asia]] |language=km |date=2014-07-09 |accessdate=2014-07-09 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126015720/https://www.rfa.org/khmer/news/politics/vn-denies-apoligize-khmerkrom-07082014224017.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。金邊市當局隨後驅散示威者，引致10人受傷<ref>{{cite web |url=http://khmer.voanews.com/content/angry-student-protestors-clash-with-police/1953517.html |script-title=km:បាតុកម្មសុំឱ្យស្ថានទូតវៀតណាមសុំទោស រងការបង្ក្រាប |date=2014-07-09 |publisher=[[美國之音|Voice of America]] |author=Reaksmey, Heng |accessdate=2014-07-09 |language=km |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305033015/http://khmer.voanews.com/content/angry-student-protestors-clash-with-police/1953517.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年7月15日，約有200名反對派示威者在金邊自由廣場遊行。當時出現了暴力事件，不過情況和以前不同：{{en-link|隆邊區|Daun Penh District}}保安部隊被示威者毒打，令至少8名警衛受傷。留院治理的警衛說要為自己伸張正義，並譴責反對派施暴。示威領袖[[莫淑華|莫淑華]]等6名反對派當選議員被捕<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/video/guards-beaten-senseless |title=Guards beaten senseless |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=2014-07-15 |accessdate=2014-07-17 |archive-date=2020-12-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211140903/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/video/guards-beaten-senseless |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/six-cnrp-members-jail |title=Six CNRP members in jail |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=2014-07-17 |accessdate=2014-07-17 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126171830/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/six-cnrp-members-jail |dead-url=no }}</ref>。金邊市法院在7月17日傳召根索卡<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/sokha-summonsed-over-violence |title=Sokha summonsed over violence |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=17 July 2014 |accessdate=17 July 2014 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126145721/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/sokha-summonsed-over-violence |dead-url=no }}</ref>。7月19日，反對派領袖桑蘭西結束長達一個月的[[歐洲|歐洲]]之旅，返回柬埔寨，並在當月22日與首相洪森會面<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/talks-07202014220938.html |title=Cambodian Parties Agree to Hold Talks to End 'Deepening' Political Crisis |publisher=Radio Free Asia |date=2014-07-20 |accessdate=2014-07-21 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124161725/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/talks-07202014220938.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。救國黨同意參與國會，結束柬埔寨史上最久的政治危機<ref name="end">{{cite web |url=http://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/political-deadlock-broken |title=Political deadlock broken |publisher=The Phnom Penh Post |date=2014-07-22 |accessdate=2014-07-22 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124144507/https://www.phnompenhpost.com/national/political-deadlock-broken |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 後續事件 ==
人民黨、救國黨在示威結束後簽訂協議，各自分擔國民議會的領袖職務。國民議會第一副主席將由救國黨議員擔任，而第二副主席則由人民黨議員擔任。國會10個專責委員會中，反對黨將出掌其中5個專責委員會（包括新成立的反貪污委員會；國民議會一共設有10個專責委員會）<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodian-opposition-gets-parliamentary-commission-roles/2428418.html |title=Cambodian Opposition Gets Parliamentary Commission Roles |publisher=[[Voice_of_America|Voice of America]] |first=Robert |last=Carmichael |date=2014-08-26 |accessdate=2014-10-04 |archive-date=2016-03-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160317200846/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodian-opposition-gets-parliamentary-commission-roles/2428418.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另外，本來被當局禁止參選的桑蘭西也成為了國會議員<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/parliament-07252014195620.html |title=Cambodian Opposition Leader Accepted as MP Ahead of Parliament Sitting |publisher=[[自由亞洲電台|Radio Free Asia]] |date=2014-07-25 |accessdate=2014-10-04 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126230748/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/parliament-07252014195620.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。反對派議員於2014年8月5日在王宮宣誓就職<ref>{{cite web |url=http://phnompenhpost.com/national/leadership-elections-set |title=Leadership elections set |work=The Phnom Penh Post |first=Kevin |last=Ponniah |date=2014-08-26 |accessdate=2014-10-04 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124123307/https://phnompenhpost.com/national/leadership-elections-set |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國際反應 ==
[[聯合國|聯合國]]和[[美國國務院|美國國務院]]都譴責柬埔寨暴力鎮壓示威<ref>{{cite news|last=Meyn|first=Colin|title=Government Blasted for Eviction of Freedom Park|url=http://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/government-blasted-for-eviction-of-freedom-park-50132/|accessdate=2014-01-06|newspaper=The Cambodia Daily|date=2014-01-06|archive-date=2019-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611035303/https://www.cambodiadaily.com/news/government-blasted-for-eviction-of-freedom-park-50132/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://khmer.voanews.com/content/us-state-department-condemn-violence-on-protestors-in-cambodia/1823211.html|title=US State Department Condemn Violence on Protestors in Cambodia|publisher=''VOA News''|author=Men Kimseng|date=2014-01-04|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305083644/http://khmer.voanews.com/content/us-state-department-condemn-violence-on-protestors-in-cambodia/1823211.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Cambodia: UN expert urges restraint as police fire on striking garment workers|url=http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=46869&Cr=protest&Cr1=#.UspHjahfvuU|work=UN News Centre|accessdate=2014-01-06|archive-date=2016-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160730071604/http://www.un.org/apps/news/story.asp?NewsID=46869&Cr=protest&Cr1=#.UspHjahfvuU|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國國會議員[[埃德·羅伊斯|埃德·羅伊斯]]呼籲洪森下台，說「洪森是時候結束自己掌權30年的局面，辭職下台」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/us-house-foreign-affairs-chair-calls-for-hun-sen-to-step-down/1824339.html|title=US House Foreign Affairs Chair Calls for Hun Sen To Step Down|publisher=''VOA News''|author=Sok Khemara|date=2014-01-07|accessdate=2014-01-30|archive-date=2016-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160323122354/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/us-house-foreign-affairs-chair-calls-for-hun-sen-to-step-down/1824339.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。逾500名[[柬埔寨裔美國人|柬埔寨裔美國人]]在[[白宮|白宮]]前方示威，尋求美國政府援助。他們又要求柬埔寨當局釋放23名在警察鎮壓示威期間被捕的人士<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodian-americans-protest-outside-white-house/1834500.html|title=Cambodian-Americans Protest Outside White House|publisher=''VOA News''|date=2014-01-21|accessdate=2014-01-30|author=Men Kimseng|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322071533/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodian-americans-protest-outside-white-house/1834500.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。聯合國柬埔寨人權狀況特別報告員{{en-link|蘇里亞·蘇貝迪|Surya Subedi}}在當局鎮壓示威後訪問柬埔寨，與洪森會晤<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/violence-01082014183929.html|title=UN Rights Envoy to Visit Cambodia in Wake of Deadly Crackdown|publisher=''Radio Free Asia''|date=2014-01-08|accessdate=2014-01-30|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124183738/https://www.rfa.org/english/news/cambodia/violence-01082014183929.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

桑蘭西在1月29日前往[[日內瓦|日內瓦]]，總部設於當地的聯合國人權理事會當時正在回顧柬埔寨的人權紀錄<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodia-at-un-to-defend-rights-record/1839449.html|title=Cambodia at UN to Defend Rights Record|publisher=''VOA News''|date=2014-01-29|accessdate=2014-01-30|author=Sok Khemara|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322102039/http://www.voacambodia.com/content/cambodia-at-un-to-defend-rights-record/1839449.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[歐盟|歐盟]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]、[[德國|德國]]、[[波蘭|波蘭]]、[[日本|日本]]和[[泰國|泰國]]都對柬埔寨的人權狀況表示關注和擔憂<ref>{{cite web|url=http://khmer.voanews.com/content/international-community-wants-cambodia-to-improve-rights-record-khmer/1840505.html|title=International Community Wants Cambodia to Improve Rights Record|publisher=''VOA Khmer''|author=Kong Sothanarith|date=2014-01-30|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006194822/http://khmer.voanews.com/content/international-community-wants-cambodia-to-improve-rights-record-khmer/1840505.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://khmer.voanews.com/content/international-community-criticize-human-rights-in-cambodia/1839664.html|title=International Community Criticize Human Rights in Cambodia|publisher=''VOA Khmer''|date=2014-01-29|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304233043/http://khmer.voanews.com/content/international-community-criticize-human-rights-in-cambodia/1839664.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]則呼籲聯合國向柬埔寨政府施壓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://khmer.voanews.com/content/human-rights-watch-condemns-weekend-cambodia-violence-khmer/1838850.html|title=Human Rights Watch Condemns Weekend Cambodia Violence|publisher=''VOA Khmer''|author=Kong Sothanarith|date=2014-01-28|accessdate=2014-07-11|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305113310/http://khmer.voanews.com/content/human-rights-watch-condemns-weekend-cambodia-violence-khmer/1838850.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[中華人民共和國|中華人民共和國]][[中華人民共和國外交部|外交部]][[中華人民共和國外交部發言人|發言人]][[華春瑩|華春瑩]]表示，中國當局希望柬埔寨各方重視國家、民族利益，以和平方式表達訴求，並藉助協商化解分歧<ref>{{cite news|author=张媛、熊争艳|url=http://intl.ce.cn/qqss/201312/31/t20131231_2030110.shtml|title=外交部发言人：希望柬埔寨有关各方通过协商解决分歧|publisher=新華網|work=中國經濟網|date=2013-12-31|accessdate=2014-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714130133/http://intl.ce.cn/qqss/201312/31/t20131231_2030110.shtml|archive-date=2014-07-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

